              Geld Sparen
            </h3>
            <p class="md:text-lg">
              Strom bleibt Strom. Sparen Sie jeden Monat bares Geld.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 drop-shadow-flat-light xl:p-8 2xl:p-10"
          >
            <svg
              stroke="currentColor"
              fill="currentColor"
              stroke-width="0"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              class="h-16 w-16 rounded-lg bg-sky-light p-4 lg:h-20 lg:w-20 xl:mb-4"
              height="1em"
              width="1em"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                d="M15 14s1 0 1-1-1-4-5-4-5 3-5 4 1 1 1 1h8zm-7.978-1A.261.261 0 0 1 7 12.996c.001-.264.167-1.03.76-1.72C8.312 10.629 9.282 10 11 10c1.717 0 2.687.63 3.24 1.276.593.69.758 1.457.76 1.72l-.008.002a.274.274 0 0 1-.014.002H7.022zM11 7a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4zm3-2a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0zM6.936 9.28a5.88 5.88 0 0 0-1.23-.247A7.35 7.35 0 0 0 5 9c-4 0-5 3-5 4 0 .667.333 1 1 1h4.216A2.238 2.238 0 0 1 5 13c0-1.01.377-2.042 1.09-2.904.243-.294.526-.569.846-.816zM4.92 10A5.493 5.493 0 0 0 4 13H1c0-.26.164-1.03.76-1.724.545-.636 1.492-1.256 3.16-1.275zM1.5 5.5a3 3 0 1 1 6 0 3 3 0 0 1-6 0zm3-2a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <h3
              class="mt-3 pb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-secondary md:text-2xl"
            >
              Ansprechpartner
            </h3>
            <p class="md:text-lg">
              Ansprechpartner in Sachen Strom, auch nach dem Wechsel.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 drop-shadow-flat-light xl:p-8 2xl:p-10"
          >
            <svg
              stroke="currentColor"
              fill="currentColor"
              stroke-width="0"
              viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              class="h-16 w-16 rounded-lg bg-sky-light p-4 lg:h-20 lg:w-20 xl:mb-4"
              height="1em"
              width="1em"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                d="M2.5 8a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 8.25-4.764.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.866A6.5 6.5 0 1 0 14.5 8a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0 5.5 5.5 0 1 1-11 0z"
